      <title>尽管美联储放宽政策，投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年，尽管黄金价格屡创新高且美联储开始放松货币政策，但投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金支持的交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>庞氏骗局爆发后，土耳其对银行首席执行官任期提出限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其银行业监管机构制定了一项计划，旨在限制银行高管的任期，此前，一家银行的首席执行官被指控涉嫌庞氏骗局，该银行是该国任职时间最长的银行之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市因交易员考虑中国政策前景而波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-stocks-kick-off-new-year-with-gains-as-data-awaited</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周四小幅波动，因中国经济数据疲软，给汽车和奢侈品等行业带来压力，这些行业的很大一部分销售额依赖于中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/european-stocks-kick-off-new-year-with-gains-as-data-awaited</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 08:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在今年第一个交易日上涨，焦点是美国库存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国原油库存减少报告和看涨技术指标的推动，油价在 2025 年伊始上涨至 11 月以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 23:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
